a hell of a reaction.

1053
01:14:10,380 --> 01:14:14,370
Please, please
don't do that.

1054
01:14:14,450 --> 01:14:16,820
Where's your sense
of compassion?

1055
01:14:16,890 --> 01:14:19,450
