to be so vicious?

1056
01:14:19,520 --> 01:14:23,180
Vicious?
Have you seen that tape?

1057
01:14:23,260 --> 01:14:26,060
Come on!
What's the big deal?

1058
01:14:26,130 --> 01:14:29,190
It's just a lonely man who
wanted a little excitement.

1059
01:14:29,260 --> 01:14:34,070
