1063
01:14:42,480 --> 01:14:45,470
- We're only human.
- You're sick.

1064
01:14:45,550 --> 01:14:48,980
Hello? No,
don't hang up on me!

1065
01:14:50,520 --> 01:14:54,620
- So, what'd he say?
